byline.contributor: Nick Corasaniti reported from San Jose, and Jonah Engel Bromwich from New York.
byline.original: By NICK CORASANITI and JONAH ENGEL BROMWICH

abstract: Donald Trump, during campaign rally in San Jose, Calif, excoriates Hillary Clinton in response to her speech attacking his foreign policy positions; protesters outside rally, some holding Mexican flags, clash violently with Trump's supporters.
lead_paragraph: Mr. Trump unleashed an attack on Mrs. Clinton in response to her criticism of his foreign policy, while protesters clashed with his supporters outside.

headline.main: Donald Trump Rebukes Hillary Clinton as Clash Erupts Outside Event
headline.print_headline: Clash Erupts at an Event for Trump

snippet: Mr. Trump unleashed an attack on Mrs. Clinton in response to her criticism of his foreign policy, while protesters clashed with his supporters outside.
